title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Antonov AN 225 v0.92
description:
In this video we will have a look at the Antonov AN 225 v0.92 which is one of the largest planes build ever. The aircraft is still under development but you can fly with it pretty well although some things do require some optimization. The last few builds several changes have been made to the aircraft including:

- Sim Update 7 compatibility
- Saltymod now works with the aircraft
- ability to open the doors including the nose of the aircraft

If you would like to give the addon a try yourself visit the site below to download it:
https://flightsim.to/file/14839/antonov-an-225-mrija-v0-5
